                        <p class="bigger-text" dbid="657ae1eba789759594df07cd"><![CDATA[Principles, Patterns and Practices are sometimes referred to as the three "Ps", and the three "Ps" are all interrelated. Practices should refer to Patterns, and Patterns that should refer to Principles.]]></p>
